-1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 356 "2.  Numbers Game.  Play the Nu
mbers Game with the base set of numbers \{2, 3, 4\}.  I.e., determine \+
how many of the integers between 0 and 20 (inclusively) can be generat
ed by calculations on the base numbers usings the operators +,-,*,/,^,
! .  In each calculation, at least two of the base numbers must be use
d and no base number can be used more than once." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
